WEBVTT

00:00:00.889 --> 00:00:03.768
Moyshe Geguzhinskis, VILNUS, LITVA.

00:00:09.327 --> 00:00:11.177
vaytert vi ikh gedenk

00:00:12.988 --> 00:00:14.495
ven s'hot bay mir pasirt

00:00:14.495 --> 00:00:24.289
der ⟨umendlekhe⟩ ume- ume- ume- um- um- der u- der der nit keyn ven s'hot nit ayngegebn tsu arbetn vayter in dem ze- magazin,

00:00:25.307 --> 00:00:27.624
un ikh bin nokh dertsu geven a komyugist,

00:00:27.624 --> 00:00:30.515
ikh hob gehert tsu a komyugisher organizatsye fun dem handls-opteylung,

00:00:31.264 --> 00:00:34.498
hot men mir aroysgerufn oyf a farzamlung fun Komyug.

00:00:35.061 --> 00:00:37.282
der sekretar fun Komyug iz bay undz geven

00:00:38.605 --> 00:00:43.880
a yidisher yat, vifl ikh gedenk Yankl Zhin hot er geheysn.

00:00:46.671 --> 00:00:54.613
er hot gehat a feikeyt er hot a feikeyt tsum sheyn tsum redn, er iz geven a vunderbar orator.

00:00:54.889 --> 00:01:00.978
un di khevre, di komyugistn, flegn im kukn poshet in moyl arayn, vi azoy er flegt reydn,

00:01:00.978 --> 00:01:04.636
vi azoy oys- oysnutsn zayne oratorishe feikeytn.

00:01:05.335 --> 00:01:08.653
di farzamlung iz geven a spetsyele. m'hot aroysgerufn mir,

00:01:09.418 --> 00:01:13.057
m'hot, un der Zhidn, Yankl Zhidn, hot bashlosn

00:01:13.485 --> 00:01:16.567
er hot shoyn gekrogn onvayzungen mistome fun dem Shtromen,

00:01:17.097 --> 00:01:23.976
az ikh hob gehat a ⟨feler⟩ heyst tsu zogn, ikh hob es ikh hob s'hot bay mir gefelt in magazin un m'darf mikh bashtrofn derfar.

00:01:24.471 --> 00:01:28.400
hot er forgeleygt az m'zol mir oysshlisn fun Komyu- fun Komyug.

00:01:28.400 --> 00:01:30.574
m'hot mikh poshet aroysgevorfn fun Komyug.

00:01:31.339 --> 00:01:36.330
er hot geredt aroysgeshtelt er hot er hot aroysgetrotn mit aza min sharfe rede kegn mir,

00:01:36.330 --> 00:01:44.871
un gezogt "⟨vot⟩ vi azoy ken a sovetisher komyugist zikh farnemen mit azelkhene zakhn? vu iz farfaln gevorn di gelt?" un azoy vayter. ikh hob zikh farentfert az

00:01:44.871 --> 00:01:48.106
ikh bin geven poshet, ikh hob nit gehat keyn derfarnkeyt in dem,

00:01:48.191 --> 00:01:55.000
un ikh hob nit gevust vi ontsuhoybn handlen, vi tsum ton, vi tsum firn a magazin, un s'hot pasirt mit mir aza min faln, nit mit mayn eygenem viln.

00:01:56.854 --> 00:02:03.918
nor s'hot keyn zakh nit geholfn, kentik er hot shoyn gekrogn a sh- gevise onvayzungen m'zol mir fun dem Komyug aroystraybn. m'hot mir fun dortn aroysgetribn.

00:02:04.347 --> 00:02:08.171
ikh ibn aroys fun der farzamlung a farfintsterter,

00:02:09.729 --> 00:02:12.511
geferlekh, mit a geferlekher mit a geferlekher shtimung,

00:02:12.511 --> 00:02:17.317
ikh gedenk ikh bin arayngegangen in kafe Asta, un ikh hob dortn,

00:02:19.078 --> 00:02:28.168
far kaas oder far far far far iberlebung, oysgetrunken dray kufl bir un tsvey un tsvey portsyes ⟨tshashiskes⟩.

00:02:29.052 --> 00:02:34.328
un in shtub bin ikh gekumen un ikh hob keynem dertseylt, vayl es iz geven a shande far mayne famil vi azoy ikh hob

00:02:34.587 --> 00:02:40.587
nit oysgenutst azoy tsu zogn mayn mayn mayn arbet, mayn mayn mayne karyere vos ikh hob gemakht in dem magazin.

00:02:45.859 --> 00:02:52.029
mir hobn dan gelebt oyf Vayse gas, oyfn UNK oyfn grinem barg.

00:02:52.795 --> 00:03:01.546
derbay iz bay undz geven a shokhn a beker. Glabin hot er geheysn. Abe Glabin.

00:03:01.755 --> 00:03:04.967
er hot gehat tsvey zin, vifl ikh gedenk.

00:03:04.967 --> 00:03:10.136
eyn zun iz geven, der elterer zun, iz geven a sportler.

00:03:10.969 --> 00:03:13.376
a rayter, er flegt zikh farnemen mit rayter sport.

00:03:15.694 --> 00:03:19.266
un er iz geven a sheyner hoykher yung,

00:03:20.115 --> 00:03:26.063
mit a fayne figur, er flegt zeyer holt hobn zikh onton in zayn uniform fun der rayter,

00:03:26.212 --> 00:03:30.425
aroysgeyn farn gas lebn toyer, zikh avekshteln az mentshn zoln kukn oyf im.

00:03:32.046 --> 00:03:36.950
ikh vel shpeter dertseyln dem di tragedye fun dem fun dem zelbn Globin zun.

00:03:37.986 --> 00:03:42.603
der tsveyter zun, a yingerer, iz geven hot geheysn Dodik Glabin.

00:03:43.673 --> 00:03:46.800
er iz oykh geven a komyugist, oykh a umlegaler komyugist,

00:03:46.800 --> 00:03:50.079
mir flegn zikh mit im trefn in di in zayendik in Komyug nokh.

00:03:50.727 --> 00:03:56.239
un ven s'gekumen di sovetn makht hot men im oykh bashtimt als komisar

00:03:56.413 --> 00:03:59.832
fun a groysn magazin in Kovne, Arkus, dos magazin hot geheysn.

00:04:00.193 --> 00:04:03.056
di firme Arkus iz geven barimt in Kovne.

00:04:04.092 --> 00:04:09.114
oyf ⟨Layses Aleye⟩ oyfn tsenter shtot iz geven a magazin fun manufaktur,

00:04:10.403 --> 00:04:15.358
un der zelber Dodik, der yunger Dodik, iz gevorn der komisar.

00:04:20.545 --> 00:04:23.948
nu vegn zikh ken ikh nor zogn vegn dem az nokh dem

00:04:24.122 --> 00:04:26.512
ven m'hot mir aroysget- aroysgetribn fun Komyug,

00:04:27.413 --> 00:04:32.739
hob ikh gevelt zikh fun dest vegn vayter aynordenen un arbetn vayter, UNK arbetn.

00:04:33.370 --> 00:04:40.434
ikh bin avek arbetn, UNK ersht bin ikh, hob ikh zikh bin ikh avek ler- lernen oyf kursn,oyf tekhnishe kursn.

00:04:40.626 --> 00:04:44.855
als tekhnik, als mekhanik volt ikh gezogt, beser oprufn.

00:04:45.351 --> 00:04:54.390
zikh tsugreytn tsu, di tekhnishe kursn flegn tsu- tsugreytn zeyer shiler tsu di fabrikn

00:04:54.835 --> 00:04:57.849
velkhe hobn velkhe hobn ekzistirt dan in Kovne.

00:04:58.530 --> 00:05:04.872
ikh hob geendikt di kursn un m'hot mir avekgeshikt arbetn in a fabrikl aza min,

00:05:04.872 --> 00:05:06.962
a mekhanishe fabrik in Lishantshey.

00:05:08.115 --> 00:05:15.281
s'hot zikh ongerufn Mekhanishe Fabrik, azoy hot es geheysn, Mekhanishe Fabrik.

00:05:16.249 --> 00:05:19.500
ikh hob zikh glaykh genumen mitn fayer in hant, ikh hob shoyn farshtanen

00:05:19.742 --> 00:05:22.790
a UNK tsu zogn, vi ruft men oyf yidish?

00:05:22.847 --> 00:05:25.120
a a tseykhenung.

00:05:23.287 --> 00:05:24.734
a tseykhenung.

00:05:25.142 --> 00:05:28.679
ikh hob zikh farinteresirt vegn shloseray arbet,

00:05:29.462 --> 00:05:33.033
un mir iz es shoyn bald gefeln gevorn. in ovnt

00:05:33.090 --> 00:05:37.590
fleg ikh nokh geyn oyf kursn, farsheyde kursn, ovnt kursn,

00:05:37.596 --> 00:05:40.830
tsu derlernen zikh vos ikh hob nit derlernt zikh in gimnazye,

00:05:41.680 --> 00:05:47.152
un mir iz es shoyn bald gefeln di gantse arbet in der tsayt. mayn foter hot shoyn dan gearbet in an hotel,

00:05:47.152 --> 00:05:53.751
er iz arayn in a in a hotel arbetn, er iz er hot farbesert, s'hot zikh bay undz farbesert, di materyele lage,

00:05:53.751 --> 00:05:55.410
er hot shoyn fardint nit shlekht.

00:05:55.551 --> 00:06:05.242
ikh gedenk mayn foter flegt oft kumen a freylekher in shtub, er hot oys- aroysgetrotn mit a deklamatsye fun fun Mayekovskin.

00:06:05.242 --> 00:06:07.374
er hot geven a ⟨liberer⟩ fun literatur.

00:06:12.156 --> 00:06:14.816
vi hot ir getrofn di milkhome?

00:06:12.510 --> 00:06:13.398
un,

00:06:15.109 --> 00:06:18.208
un do ot vil ikh vegn dem zogn,

00:06:18.754 --> 00:06:32.450
un do arbetndik in dem Mekhanishn in Mekhanishe UNK Mekhanishe, volt ikh gezogt vi ontsurufn, Verkshtat azoy hot geheysn, Mekhanishe Verkshtat hobn zey geheysn.

00:06:33.351 --> 00:06:36.686
ot do iz hot zikh ongehoybn un a i-

00:06:37.502 --> 00:06:44.010
bay tog iz geven, vifl ikh gedenk, iz men aroysgegangen fun undzer tsekh,

00:06:45.265 --> 00:06:51.570
hobn mir gehert vi iz men hot ongehoybn bom- gehert vi es faln bombes iber Kovner gasn.

00:06:52.858 --> 00:06:57.409
emes un s'hot ongehoybn un fun vaytn hot zikh geher- hot zikh gezen a groyser roykh.

00:06:58.123 --> 00:07:02.765
un ikh nit zikh oryentirt fun velkher zayt hot men hot men bombardirt. oder hot men bombardirt

00:07:02.845 --> 00:07:07.207
dem grinem barg vu lebn dortn, ikh hob shoyn moyre gehat far mayne eltern vu ikh hob zey gelozn.

00:07:07.658 --> 00:07:11.398
oder men hot bombardirt Shantser kazarmes, oder andersh vu.

00:07:11.725 --> 00:07:15.516
nor eyn zakh iz geven, der Partog hot undz organizirt

00:07:15.943 --> 00:07:21.928
az mir zoln grobn grobn grobns azelkhene far unter,

00:07:21.968 --> 00:07:26.335
oystsu- oystsubaha- bahaltn zikh fun di bombes azoy, in in azelkhene grobns,

00:07:26.335 --> 00:07:29.286
fardekte grobns oystsu- zikh oystsubahaltn fun di bombes.

00:07:29.629 --> 00:07:37.723
mir hobn glaykh genumen azoy. ikh hob genumen glaykh a lopete in hantl ale di glu- komyugistn mit di komunistn velkhe hobn, fun dem fun dem fun di fun di UNK,

00:07:38.353 --> 00:07:41.469
fun di verkshtatn, hobn zikh glaykh genumen tsu der arbet.

00:07:41.593 --> 00:07:51.105
mir hobn gearbet a gantse nakht, un f- di gantse nakht hot zikh gehert hobn mir gehert shiserayen farsheydene,

00:07:51.415 --> 00:07:55.799
mir hobn farshtanen di krig hot zikh ongehoybn. men darf zen vos iz tsum ton.

00:07:55.799 --> 00:08:00.234
mir hobn zikh nit forgeshtelt az di krig vet brengen aza min umglik oyf undz.

00:08:00.544 --> 00:08:07.086
mir hobn gemeynt az mir veln kenen helfn farteydikn zikh fun di fashistn.

00:08:07.783 --> 00:08:12.451
un es vet gikh endikn di krig. nor s'hot zikh aroysgevizn punkt farkert.

00:08:12.981 --> 00:08:21.480
ikh gedenk nokh grobndik di shuts-grobns, hot men zenen mir geven zenen mir geblibn on produktn.

00:08:22.465 --> 00:08:28.655
mentshn zenen geven hungerik. ibergebn far der arbet, un m'hot nit gevust vos tsum ton.

00:08:28.655 --> 00:08:32.806
hot men bashlosn mir, azoy vi ikh hob gehat a velosiped an eygenem,

00:08:32.806 --> 00:08:35.975
hot men bashlosn mir aroystsushikn in a bekeray

00:08:36.927 --> 00:08:41.089
tsum krign etlekhe leblekh broyt far di velkhe arbetn fun di shuts-grobns.

00:08:41.128 --> 00:08:44.213
ikh hob genumen mayn mayn rover heyst tsu zogn mayn velosiped

00:08:44.213 --> 00:08:46.539
oyfn grinem, ikh bin avekgeforn oyfn grinem barg.

00:08:47.423 --> 00:08:50.471
geforn bin ikh durkhn shtot vu ikh hob gezen vi es geyen

00:08:50.713 --> 00:08:57.491
es geyen es vi es geyen oder loyfn shoyn di Royte Armeyer, tseshrokene,

00:08:57.885 --> 00:09:05.236
farloyrene, eyner on a shtivl, eyner on a ro- on a on on on a hitl, on a plotke,

00:09:05.344 --> 00:09:10.198
zey hobn zey zaynen shoyn gelofn fun di grenetsn durkh der Kovner shtot,

00:09:10.390 --> 00:09:14.788
zey hobn farshtanen az zikh tsum farteydikn iz shoyn geven tsu shpet.

00:09:16.920 --> 00:09:19.226
ikh bin arayngeforn tsu in a bekeray,

00:09:19.806 --> 00:09:26.297
agev, di bekeray iz geven a private bekeray in Kovne, in oyfn grinem barg,

00:09:26.607 --> 00:09:29.267
dos iz geven a korev fun dem par- undzer partog.

00:09:29.267 --> 00:09:32.203
er hot mir gegebn dem adres, ikh zol zikh vendn tsu dem balebos fun dem

00:09:32.203 --> 00:09:34.905
bekeray, zol er mir gebn etlekhe etlekhe lebns broyt,

00:09:34.956 --> 00:09:39.830
far far di hungerike arbeter velkhe grobn di shuts- velkhe grobn di shuts-grobns.

00:09:40.140 --> 00:09:41.653
ikh bin arayn in bekeray,

00:09:41.862 --> 00:09:47.672
in hoyf, ikh geb a kuk, es shteyt a groyse od- a groyse rey shoyn fun mentshn, mentshn hobn shoyn dersh- dershpirt az s'iz a krig,

00:09:47.672 --> 00:09:50.715
un di ershte rey in a krigs-tsayt heybt on tsu feln produktn.

00:09:52.037 --> 00:09:54.700
ikh hob zikh arayngerisn in bekeray durkh a hintershtn tir,

00:09:54.700 --> 00:09:59.017
un ikh bin arayn tsum balebos mitn tsetele funem partogni, un ikh hob im gezogt, her tsu, m'darf helfn.

00:09:59.142 --> 00:10:02.429
zogt er, yo, oyber, zogt er, me- mentshn zenen hungerik, darf men helfn.

00:10:02.429 --> 00:10:05.852
nu, zogt er, keyner zol nit zen, zogt er. zoln di mentshn velkhe shteyen in rey nit zen

00:10:05.976 --> 00:10:08.738
vi ikh trog aroys e- etlekhe lebns broyt.

00:10:10.228 --> 00:10:14.238
makh dos azoy zol keyner nit zen, un ikh hob onge- ongelodn oyfn velosiped

00:10:15.105 --> 00:10:17.225
akht labns broyt hot er mir gegebn.

00:10:18.835 --> 00:10:26.163
un ikh bin geforn, ikh hob geforn tsurik tsu der arbet, tsum helfn di hungerike mentshn.

00:10:26.163 --> 00:10:31.130
ikh bin farbaygeforn di, mir hobn gelebt oyf Vayse gas, nor farbaygeforn bin ikh farbay undzer shtub.

00:10:31.812 --> 00:10:37.965
ikh bin arayn mitn velosiped bin ikh arayngeforn tsu undz shtub mit di gra- mit di akht labns broyt.

00:10:39.152 --> 00:10:44.782
in shtub iz gezesn der foter, a dershrokener farshteyt zikh, di muter un der bruder mayner,

00:10:45.278 --> 00:10:48.211
zey hobn gezen, zaynen shoyn geven, zenen oykh geven hungerik,

00:10:48.211 --> 00:10:52.915
vayl in shtot hot men shoyn produktn nit gekrogn in der tsayt, iz shoyn in magazin iz shoyn geven

00:10:52.973 --> 00:10:58.148
umetum di andere farmakht, oder s'iz geven shoyn a moyre aroystsugeyn,

00:10:59.638 --> 00:11:03.665
zogt tsu mir di muter, efsher vestu iberlozn undz eyn labn broyt. UNK

00:11:03.908 --> 00:11:08.494
khuts far undzer undzer mishpokhe. zog ikh, neyn, ikh ken dos nit ton.

00:11:08.494 --> 00:11:13.132
di labns broyt zaynen bashtimt gevorn far undzere arbayter velkhe arbaytn in di shuts-grobns.

00:11:13.543 --> 00:11:18.516
zogt tsu mir der foter, "Meyshl, farshtey, mir zaynen aleyn dokh oykh hungerike.

00:11:19.028 --> 00:11:25.569
mir betn dokh bay dir in gantsn eyn labn. fun akht labns vest vest avektrogn avektrogn f- zibn, s'nit azoy geferlekh."

00:11:25.896 --> 00:11:27.105
ikh hob zikh opgezogt.

00:11:27.364 --> 00:11:33.064
ikh bin geven azoy fanatish geshtimt az ikh hob zikh nit gegebn ikh hob nit gegebn ibergelozn keyn eyn labn far mayn mishpokhe,

00:11:33.064 --> 00:11:39.629
un ikh hob genumen di velosiped mit di ongelodene broyt un avekgefirt dortn in di Mekhanishe Varshtatn,

00:11:39.629 --> 00:11:42.292
tsu mayne a- mit-arbeter.

00:11:45.994 --> 00:11:47.962
mir hobn vider gearbet di gantse nakht,

00:11:48.576 --> 00:11:52.637
un do hot zikh do gehert di shiserayen shoyn,

00:11:53.470 --> 00:11:57.784
di bombes zenen shoyn gefaln nit vayt fun fun undz, ikh hob bashlosn,

00:11:58.026 --> 00:12:03.048
ikh hob gezen az di arbeter un der partog aleyn hot zikh dershrokn, men darf loyfn.

00:12:03.055 --> 00:12:07.590
loyfn tsu di fun danent. antloyfn fun di fashistn.

00:12:07.590 --> 00:12:10.743
tsu di sovetishe grenetsn, tsu der grenets fun Rusland.

00:12:11.914 --> 00:12:15.941
ikh hob genumen mayn, ikh hob genumen mayn velosiped,

00:12:16.977 --> 00:12:21.226
ikh hob zikh avekgezetst oyf im un ikh bin geforn tsu der ersh- der ershter rey in shtub a kuk ton vos

00:12:21.226 --> 00:12:28.158
vos vi vil vos tuen dort mayne eltern. ikh bin geven zeyer umruik tsulib di tsulib in tsayt fun krig.

00:12:28.958 --> 00:12:32.681
ikh bin avekgeforn in shtub, oyfn grinem gas oyf Vayse gas,

00:12:32.907 --> 00:12:36.984
ikh bin arayngegangen in shtub, zey hobn mir zikh zeyer UNK, zikh zeyer shtark derfreyt,

00:12:37.716 --> 00:12:40.697
vos ikh leb nokh, vayl in yener tsayt zenen zeyer fil umgekumen.

00:12:42.373 --> 00:12:51.429
s'hot zikh ongehoybn dan bavayzn in di gasn banditn, mit vayse bender ongeton.

00:12:52.330 --> 00:12:57.251
zenen geven fun di lit- litvishe shuts-politsey velkhe hobn mitgearbet mit di daytshe mit di daytshe fashistn.

00:12:57.493 --> 00:13:02.871
zey in der ershter rey hobn ongehoybn roybn in di yidishe shtiber,

00:13:02.961 --> 00:13:09.249
zey hobn ongehoybn shisn, in der ershter, volt ikh gezogt, tsu ersht baroybn un dan dershisn.

00:13:11.010 --> 00:13:16.314
s'gevorn di yidishe bafelkerung in Kovne hot hot zikh shoyn ongehoybn bau- zeyer shtark baumruikn.

00:13:16.314 --> 00:13:19.307
a teyl hobn onge- zenen antlofn fun di heymen antlofn,

00:13:20.072 --> 00:13:23.157
der eyntsiker veg iz geven tsu rateven dem lebn iz geven Rusland.

00:13:23.157 --> 00:13:25.533
dos heyst in in Sovetn Farband.

00:13:25.911 --> 00:13:35.037
nor oyfn veg zaynen zeyer fil umgekumen. m'hot zey gekhapt, m'hot zey dershosn. mayn familye hot

00:13:35.037 --> 00:13:39.253
hot oykh gevolt zikh evakuirn, nor zey hobn gevart oyf mir, zey hobn on mir nit gevolt antloyfn.

00:13:40.086 --> 00:13:43.930
nor vi ikh bin ven ikh bin shoyn gekumen in shtub, un zey hobn mikh derzen,

00:13:43.930 --> 00:13:47.708
hobn zey bashlosn m'hot bashlosn ersht veln mir ale tsuzamen veln mir loyfn.

00:13:48.068 --> 00:13:50.976
nor mayn muter hot zikh oyfgehaltn, zogt zi, veystu vos, efsher

00:13:50.976 --> 00:13:54.407
vet men undz nit tshepenen. fun dest vegn mir zenen nit keyn raykhe yidishe familye,

00:13:54.615 --> 00:13:58.473
m'vet undz, mir zaynen, mir hobn keyn mol keyn shlekhts nit geton keynem,

00:13:58.480 --> 00:14:05.494
m'vet efsher undz lozn lebn. un der loyfn iz shoyn kentik geven

00:14:06.428 --> 00:14:11.518
nit volt ikh gezogt shoyn ni- s'hot shoyn nit gehat keyn keyn zin.

00:14:12.115 --> 00:14:16.783
vayl azoy mir hobn shoyn gehert a sakh fun undzere shkheynim zenen gelofn un zey hobn zikh geklert tsurik,

00:14:17.582 --> 00:14:20.293
oder hobn farloyrn zeyer mishpokhes, zeyere

00:14:21.058 --> 00:14:25.316
mitglider fun mishpokhes. fun a fun a mishpokhe iz gekumen tsu geyn tsvey oder dray mentshn,

00:14:25.316 --> 00:14:30.142
un ven di mishpokhe iz geven finef zeks. un di ib- eyn a groysn teyl zenen umgekumen oyfn veg, oder m'hot zey dershosn.

00:14:30.142 --> 00:14:36.577
ho'mir bashlosn zikh oysbahaltn in in undzer heym, in undzer shtub dortn, in a kleyn shtibl.

00:14:37.191 --> 00:14:39.885
durkhn fentster hobn mir gezen vi es loyfn arum di banditn,

00:14:39.908 --> 00:14:43.884
loyfn arum di fashistn, un zukhn yidishe mentshn.

00:14:46.388 --> 00:14:52.489
mir hobn zikh bahaltn oyf a boydem, opgelegn oyfn boydem etlekhe teg.

00:14:52.700 --> 00:14:57.742
genumen tsum zukh etle- kartofl ober m'hot gehat, a bisl hot men gezukht dortn groypn gedint,

00:14:57.742 --> 00:15:02.274
bay di shkheynim hobn undz geholfn. un mir hobn zikh bahaltn.

00:15:02.274 --> 00:15:07.728
un ibergevart di shkhites vos iz forgekumen oyf yener gas fun Vayse.

00:15:10.975 --> 00:15:13.922
un do farshteyt zikh di tsayt iz gegangen

00:15:15.143 --> 00:15:18.157
un m'hot ongehoybn tsu reydn az di yidn vet men aroystraybn fun shtot.

00:15:18.180 --> 00:15:24.350
m'vet zey aynordenen, m'vet zey arayn- m'vet zey bazetsn in a geto.

00:15:25.504 --> 00:15:32.796
in Kovne, in in Slabodke iz geven a ort aza min a a a Slabodker vinkl vos hobn gelebt

00:15:32.796 --> 00:15:36.668
der oremster der orem- der oremster teyl fun der litvisher bafelkerung,

00:15:36.895 --> 00:15:40.669
un dortn hot men hobn mir gehert vet vet vern bashtimt far a geto.

00:15:41.772 --> 00:15:43.909
nor mir hobn zikh nit geaylt tsu forn in geto.

00:15:43.999 --> 00:15:46.476
mir hobn nokh gemeynt, mir hobn nokh gehoft, efsher veln mir

00:15:46.476 --> 00:15:50.591
kenen oysmaydn, efsher vet nokh kumen di Royte Armey tsurik, un zi vet undz bafrayen.

00:15:52.200 --> 00:15:53.932
nor umzist iz geven undzer vartn,

00:15:55.018 --> 00:16:00.525
vayle produktn tsum koyfn in magazin hobn mir shoyn nit gehat, nit far vos,

00:16:00.525 --> 00:16:04.091
un mir shoyn hobn moyre gehat aroystsugeyn afile in tsu zikh shteln in rey,

00:16:04.114 --> 00:16:10.000
vayle m'hot yidishe penemer in der rey flegt men glaykh derkenen,

00:16:10.066 --> 00:16:17.024
un di ikh volt gezogt di fashistn flegn undz glaykh flegn glaykh aroysnemen fun di reyen in di reyen

00:16:17.024 --> 00:16:24.662
un oder gut on tsu shlogn, gebn klep, oder avekfirn oyf di ⟨fyordn⟩ tsu dershisn.

00:16:28.397 --> 00:16:38.769
ikh gedenk az in undzer shtub iz gekumen tsu forn a dorf mentsh eyner, mit a vogn mit kartofl.

00:16:40.682 --> 00:16:46.510
er iz arayn tsu undz in shtub, un er hot gezogt, efsher hobn mir ge- gevise vert zakhn.

00:16:46.565 --> 00:16:53.182
er vet kenen helfn mit gebn, er vet kenen undz gebn kartofl. er hot gevust az mir zenen hungerik un mir hobn nit vos tsum esn.

00:16:53.642 --> 00:17:00.988
gedenk ikh, m'hot gehat a ney mashin, a Zinger ney mashin, velkhe mir hobn gekoyft grod far der tsayt far farn krig,

00:17:00.988 --> 00:17:04.278
oyf oystsutsoln hobn mir es genumen ge- fun der firme Zinger.

00:17:04.278 --> 00:17:06.107
mir hobn nokh far in gantsn nit batsolt.

00:17:07.092 --> 00:17:11.507
der di mashin iz geven a naye. mayn mame flegt oft oyf ir neyen.

00:17:14.112 --> 00:17:19.016
nu, mayn foter hot ober az di az mir hobn keyn anderer oysveg nit,

00:17:19.140 --> 00:17:26.508
hot er genumen di ney-mashin, un far di ney-mashin hobn mir gekrogn fun dem fun dem poyer fun dorf a zak mit kartofl. dos iz far undz geven a groyser

00:17:26.835 --> 00:17:32.601
a groyser azoy tsu zogn a groyser glik vos mir hobn gekent oy- khotsh esn vos nit iz.

00:17:32.978 --> 00:17:37.427
a tsveytn fal gedenk ikh ven ikh hob ven s'hot zikh geendikt bay undz di kartofl,

00:17:39.019 --> 00:17:43.841
hob ikh genumen hob ikh genumen di mame's kley- di mame's di mame hot far zikh zikh ongegreyt

00:17:43.841 --> 00:17:48.058
a opshnit fun a fun a opshnit tsum tsu neyen a kleyd.

00:17:49.212 --> 00:17:52.499
s'iz geven zeyer a sheyner a sheyner farb fun di kleyd.

00:17:52.499 --> 00:17:56.423
zi hot alemen getroymt vegn dem az zi vet oys- oyfneyen far zikh a naye kleyd,

00:17:56.423 --> 00:18:02.083
un zi vet, vi a froy hot zi UNK hot zi zeyer zeyer ge- zeyer holt gehat di di shtof.

00:18:02.273 --> 00:18:09.793
nor ikh hob es genumen ikh hob genumen, nor azoy vi mir hobn keyn esn nit gehat, un der f- di muter iz geven azoy nit keyn shtark aktive in dem zin, der foter iz geven zeyer shtark tsebrokhn

00:18:09.951 --> 00:18:14.829
nokh dem vos er hot er hot gezen di gantse lage fun di krig, hob ikh genumen di shtik di di mame's

00:18:14.927 --> 00:18:20.969
shtof fun di kleyd un ikh hob avekgetrogn oyfn avekgetrogn oyf geheym oyf a merkl,

00:18:22.219 --> 00:18:28.305
ikh hob zikh aroysgekhapt fun shtub, un ikh bin nit geven enlekh tsu keyn yidn, mayn oyszen iz geven a vi a a geven a heler yat,

00:18:28.547 --> 00:18:32.574
vi vi nit keyn yid un ikh bin ant- avekgelofn in a oyf a merkl,

00:18:32.633 --> 00:18:37.527
un ikh hob do avekgegebn far far di sh- un ikh hob avekgegebn di sh- di mame's kleyd, mame's kleydn-shtof

00:18:37.527 --> 00:18:42.584
far a shtikl khazer fleysh. un ikh hob gebrakht in shtub.

00:18:42.584 --> 00:18:45.062
ikh hob gemeynt ikh hob geton a groyse arbet

00:18:45.085 --> 00:18:50.124
far mayn mishpokhe zi zol nit kenen hungern. nor di mame hot gezen,

00:19:16.894 --> 00:19:19.588
ikh vel aykh brengen efsher a vaser.

00:19:18.761 --> 00:19:24.953
neyn. neyn UNK.

00:19:29.753 --> 00:19:32.919
nu ikh hob keyn breyre nit gehat, ikh hob gemuzt helfn in shtub.

00:19:34.545 --> 00:19:40.276
un do iz gekumen di tsayt ven mir hobn gemuzt a- aroys- aroysforn fun heym.

00:19:41.953 --> 00:19:46.233
m'hot ongelodn oyf a fur velkhe mir hobn gekrogn bay a shokhn,

00:19:46.594 --> 00:19:53.186
onge- ongelodn di bisl beberkes vos iz do geblibn un mir zaynen avekgeforn

00:19:53.327 --> 00:19:57.084
arayngeforn in geto in dem o- in Slabodke in geto.

00:20:01.343 --> 00:20:03.733
in geto farshteyt zikh geven shvere tsayt,

00:20:04.667 --> 00:20:10.179
di ershte zakh iz geven di ershte frage iz geven di problem fun fun esn fun hunger.

00:20:13.155 --> 00:20:23.915
in geto hot zikh hot zikh di ongehoybn s- di geto iz gevorn fartsamt unter a groysn tsoym, s'hot zikh in gantsn farmakht,

00:20:25.069 --> 00:20:28.457
un men- di yi- day- daytsher flegn kumen gants oft

00:20:28.457 --> 00:20:34.212
oystsu- farshafn oysfirn farshidene aktsyes, do nemen toyznt man oder fir hundert man,

00:20:34.212 --> 00:20:39.474
do ayn- do a gantsn kvartir flegn zey oyfshnaydn, un avekfirn oyf di fyordn tsu dershisn.

00:20:41.640 --> 00:20:49.062
undz undzer mishpokhe fun dest vegn oys, mir hobn gelebt in geto, in in same breg fun geto, un tsu undz flegt grod

00:20:49.062 --> 00:20:54.055
nit dergeyn di aktsyes, di ershte a- di ershte aktsyes vos iz forgekumen in geto.

00:20:54.263 --> 00:21:00.652
nor vos, mir hobn m'hot dor- di daytshn hobn organizirt arbeter brigades, tsu geyn arbetn bay di daytshn.

00:21:02.818 --> 00:21:12.802
s'hot zikh geshafn a yidishe politsey, s'hot zikh geshafn a yidishe arbets-amt, s'hot zikh geshafn yidishe sotsyale hilf, azoy hot zikh es gerufn, sotsyale hilf, zeyer a shvere, s'zeyer shvakhe sotsyale hilf iz geven,

00:21:14.597 --> 00:21:17.763
un arbetn hot men ge- UNK hot men hot men getribn.

00:21:18.040 --> 00:21:24.109
in di er- di ershte arbet iz geven oyfn Kovner erodrom, oyfn Kovner flug-plats hot er geheysn.

00:21:24.638 --> 00:21:32.006
ikh mitn foter zaynen avek arbetn oyfn Kovner erodrom.

00:21:32.957 --> 00:21:39.276
dortn hot men gearbetn tsvey shikhtn. tsvey shikhtn, volt ikh gezogt vi m'ruft es on, tsvey

00:21:39.276 --> 00:21:48.915
di ershte shikht fun in der fri flegt geyn fun zeks in der fri biz tsvey a zeyger, eyn eyn eyn shikht,

00:21:49.090 --> 00:21:52.779
un der tsveyter flegt zikh onheybn fun tsvey biz shpet bay nakht.

00:21:53.342 --> 00:22:00.002
mir iz oysgekumen tsu geyn mitn foter in tsveytn shikht, azoy tsu zogn in tsveytn teyl, vakht, dem tsveyte vakhte.

00:22:01.425 --> 00:22:04.979
m'hot undz getribn oyf Rodom, akht kilometer flegt men undz UNK traybn tsu fus,

00:22:05.644 --> 00:22:13.420
mentshn flegn geyn far gut oysgemutshete, kranke, zey hobn ge-

00:22:13.420 --> 00:22:16.711
arbetn hot men gemuzt, vayl m'hot gehoft zol krign dortn a bisl

00:22:16.711 --> 00:22:22.648
zup oder yushnikli hot men es gerufn bay undz. tsu krign vos optsuesn.

00:22:23.380 --> 00:22:26.068
un vayters hot men zikh fun di arbet nit getort aroysdreyen.

00:22:26.068 --> 00:22:30.663
vayl in arbets ⟨amt⟩ hot men gefirt a shpetsyeler KATASTER azoy tsu zogn, a shpetsyeln

00:22:31.783 --> 00:22:38.206
khezhbm ver es geyt ver es geyt tsu arbet un ver es blaybt, ver es ha- bahalt zikh oys.

00:22:39.748 --> 00:22:42.715
vayl in der brigade fun di fun dem fun dem

00:22:42.715 --> 00:22:46.779
fun dem arbets-plats hot men oykh ongetseykhnt ver es kumt tsu geyn, di familyes

00:22:47.308 --> 00:22:52.857
un in arbets-amt hot men gevust di ayn- vifl aynvoyners zenen do in geto, hobn zey glaykh

00:22:52.857 --> 00:22:55.284
kontrolirt ver es geyt tsu der arbet un ver nit.

00:22:56.421 --> 00:23:01.764
in erodrom hobn mir gearbet di nakht shikht mitn foter tsuzamen,

00:23:03.475 --> 00:23:09.223
shvere arbet. ikh gedenk di maysters velkhe zenen dortn geven, di o di vel- di di

00:23:09.364 --> 00:23:11.985
di daytshisher maysters, hot men gerufn eyner

00:23:11.985 --> 00:23:17.171
Di Vayse Hitele, velkher iz geven a geferlekher bandit, a geferlekher shloger.

00:23:19.017 --> 00:23:21.373
er flegt arumgeyn mitn shtekn in hant

00:23:22.189 --> 00:23:26.216
un ver er iz un ver un ver mentsh der yid vos flegt zikh

00:23:26.374 --> 00:23:32.100
opdreyen a mol fun der a bisl opdreyen fun der arbet, oder zikh opkern oder zikh opruen, flegt er glaykh tsu yenem tsuloyfn

00:23:32.100 --> 00:23:36.391
un klapn ibern kop. zayn arbet iz geven nor tsum klapn ibern kop.

00:23:36.702 --> 00:23:42.365
un ven nor ven ven Di Vayse Hitele flegt zikh opdreyen in a zayt, flegt men zikh kenen a bisl opotemen.

00:23:43.823 --> 00:23:48.474
di yidn hobn dan azoy tsu zogn pasiv ongehoybn a vidershtand.

00:23:48.632 --> 00:23:56.062
ven Di Vayse Hitele hot gekukt vi m- vet hot gekukt vi men arbet, flegt men zikh nemen tsu der lopete.

00:23:56.062 --> 00:24:01.400
un ven Di Vayse Hitele flegt zikh opdreyen in a zayt, flegt men avekleygn di lopete in a zayt un a bisl zikh opotemen.

00:24:01.643 --> 00:24:07.594
azoy iz geven der metod fun di yidn fun di yidishe arbayter, edro- erodromshiks azoy tsu zogn.

00:24:12.763 --> 00:24:18.501
in geto zayendik in geto hob ikh zikh getrofn mit khevre

00:24:18.501 --> 00:24:21.501
velkhe ikh hob zikh frier velkhe ikh hob zikh mit frier mit zey

00:24:21.501 --> 00:24:24.310
gehat gekhavert iber hoypt fun der Yidisher Komers-Gimnazye.

00:24:24.310 --> 00:24:31.964
di Yidishe Komers-Gimnazye iz geven a volt ikh gezogt a yidish a yidishe link-geshtimte

00:24:31.964 --> 00:24:35.610
komers-gimnazye. vayl ye- di lerer di lerer velkhe hobn dortn gelernt zenen ale geven

00:24:35.610 --> 00:24:39.886
zeyer progresiv geshtimt un zey hobn ge- oysge-

00:24:39.886 --> 00:24:45.883
oysge- volt ikh gezogt, oysgekhovet di shiler in a linkn gayst.

00:24:46.682 --> 00:24:52.650
hob ikh getrofn aza min khaver vi Elke Tenko in geto.

00:24:55.525 --> 00:25:01.358
Elke Tenko iz geven a ⟨ernster⟩ yung, a basketbolist,

00:25:02.443 --> 00:25:07.145
mit a kaltn ponem azoy, m'hot im gerufn Elke der Kalter hot men im gerufn.

00:25:08.822 --> 00:25:11.330
er hot mir arayn- er hot arayngerufn mir tsu zikh in shtub,

00:25:11.421 --> 00:25:16.933
er hot gelebt in a kleyn tsimerl, un er hot mir gezogt, veyst Meyshke,

00:25:18.542 --> 00:25:22.839
dos iz geven in dray un fertsikstn yor shoyn, in tsvey un f- tsvey un fe- oder dray un fertsikstn yor,

00:25:23.048 --> 00:25:28.813
mir viln zikh organizirn mir viln mir viln zikh organizirn in a vidershtand kegn di daytshn.

00:25:29.241 --> 00:25:32.216
vi s'vet oyszen der vidershtand hobn mir nokh nit bashlosn.

00:25:32.216 --> 00:25:37.228
nor di ershte zakh vos bay mir iz do, ikh hob, zogt er, a pistolet arayngetrogn ⟨in tog fun⟩,

00:25:37.228 --> 00:25:43.241
mitgenumen mit zikh. un er hot mir aroysgenumen, mir gevizn dem pistolet mit etlekhe koyln. zogt er, ot iz undzer

00:25:43.467 --> 00:25:45.317
gever velkhe mir hobn haynt tsum tog.

00:25:45.981 --> 00:25:48.256
ikh hob genumen dem ershtn mol in hant dem pistolet,

00:25:48.256 --> 00:25:54.361
un ikh hob farshtanen az m'darf, az s'vet zayn mit vos zikh tsu farteydikn kegn di fashistn, kegn di daytshn.

00:25:57.355 --> 00:26:03.654
mir hobn or- organizirt a kleyninkn kemerl azoy tsu zogn fun a krayzl fun etlekhe man bay Elke Tenko

00:26:03.654 --> 00:26:05.364
in shtub flegn mir zikh mir trefn.

00:26:06.197 --> 00:26:12.744
undzer arbet iz geven vegn dem ershtn zakh hobn mir batrakht dem gantsn konstruktsye fun dem pistolet.

00:26:12.765 --> 00:26:17.744
m'iz di kin- di khevre zoln kenen zikh m'kenen farshteyn vi zikh tsu farteydikn

00:26:17.744 --> 00:26:23.127
oder vi ontsugrayfn di daytshn in fal fun a fun letstn moment.

00:26:23.127 --> 00:26:37.899
un mir f- un mir flegn oft zikh trefn dortn bay im hern a umlegale radyo hot er gehat, a a radyo aparat fun Moskve.

00:26:38.412 --> 00:26:47.062
mir flegn firn a min arbet azoy tsu zogn agitatsyone ar- agitatsye arbet tsvishn di khevre.

00:26:49.617 --> 00:26:53.863
nor do in a gutn frimorgn ven ikh bin gekumen tsu Elken in shtub,

00:26:54.139 --> 00:27:01.743
hob ikh gefunen farmakht di farmakht far- farklapt di tir. ikh hob nokhgefregt di shkheynim, vos kumt do for? vu iz der Elke farfaln gevorn?

00:27:01.800 --> 00:27:07.144
vayzt zikh aroys, in der tsayt iz geven a aktsye, m'hot gefirt yidn toyznt,

00:27:08.365 --> 00:27:11.700
tsi zibn hundert dakht zikh yidn, zibn hundert yidn hot men avekgefirt in Estland.

00:27:11.841 --> 00:27:19.682
un Elke iz arayngefaln tsvishn der tsvishn der tsvishn di khe- tsvishn di mentshn di ⟨ashirim⟩ fun geto

00:27:22.523 --> 00:27:25.031
mistome mit zayn pistolet tsuzamen.

00:27:25.273 --> 00:27:32.509
azoy bin ikh ge- zenen mir geblibn vider on a on a hofenung vayter tsum ton in geto.
